    Phase 3 后端开发            :be3, 10, 13

    section Frontend Engineer
    Phase 1 前端开发 (Mock→Real) :fe1, 4, 7
    Phase 2 前端开发            :fe2, 8, 11
    Phase 3 前端开发            :fe3, 11, 14

    section Audit Engineer
    Phase 1 代码审计            :au1, 7, 8
